parameters.name: $select
parameters.description: A comma separated list of fields to return in the response.

parameters.name: $filter
parameters.description: An OData expression (an expression that returns a boolean value) using the entity's fields to retrieve a subset of the results.

parameters.name: $orderby
parameters.description: Uses a comma-separated list of expressions to sort response items. Add 'desc' for descending order, otherwise it's ascending by default.

parameters.name: $first
parameters.description: An integer value that specifies the number of items to return. Default is 100.

parameters.name: $after
parameters.description: An opaque string that specifies the cursor position after which results should be returned.
